HEADWORD: Riddle
<hw>Rid"dle</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To speak ambiguously or
enigmatically.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<persfn>Lysander</persfn> <xex>riddles</xex>
very prettily.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
